data.description: One of a kind, Large Corner Property Fully Detached located in Prime Bensonhurst. This is a Legal Two Family used as One Large Family. The Home has been well maintain and is move in ready with Three stories, Full Basement, Private Parking with a detached double car garage for more than 5+ parking space. The Home Features 5 Beds 2.5 Bath, Private Backyard, and a Side yard. Home exterior is built with beautiful Brick and Stucco design making its unique look stand out. Natural Sunlight shines through from all angles of the property, Modern style, and spacious. Very convenient location for transportation N/D Train, Bus, and near busy commercial district on 18th Avenue, Shopping and Restaurants. Will not last!
